\f0 \cf0  Let 
\f1 \cf3 $\\ol E_1^C$
\f0 \cf0  be the time 1 expected value of 
\f1 \cf3 $E_2^C$
\f0 \cf0 . Since 
\f1 \cf3 $\\ol C_1^B$
\f0 \cf0  is only ever at most 
\f1 \cf3 $D$
\f0 \cf0 , 
\f1 \cf3 $\\ol E_1^C\\le\\ol  E_1^W$
\f0 \cf0  for values of 
\f1 \cf3 $X_1$
\f0 \cf0  within a sufficiently small neighbourhood of 
\f1 \cf3 $D$
